name: GeneRat
body:
### Welcome to GeneRat.
GeneRat is a Computational Genetic Framework to provide basic genetic computational solution, such as Genetic Mapping, QTL detection, etc..., this project is created, organized and maintained by CGG-NJFU, the Computational Genetic Group of Nanjing Forestry University.

### Active Members List
```
@yiqingxu
@rhwfu
```

If you're interested to join in us, please do not hesitate to contact us
